'''Dr. Burhanuddin bin Muhammad Nur al-Hilmi''' (laia di [[Kota Bharu]], [[Perak, Malaysia]] taun 1911 - wafaik di [[Taiping (Malaysia)|Taiping]], [[Perak, Malaysia]], 25 Oktober 1969)<ref name="bio">{{cite article|title=Burhanuddin bin Muhammad Nur al-Hilmi |url=http://www.answers.com/topic/nur-al-hilmi-burhanuddin-bin-muhammad |work=[[Britannica]] |publisher=[[Answers.com]]|accessdate=June 24, 2010}}</ref> adalah pajuang kamardekaan sarato politisi dari [[Malaysia]]. Burhanuddin pernah manjabat sabagai Yang Dipertua Agung [[Parti Islam Se-Malaysia]] (PAS). Baliau tasabuik sabagai surang nasionalis radikal sarato pamikia [[Islam]].<ref>{{cite book|last1=Matheson Hooker|first1=Virginia|last2=Norani Othman|first2=|title=Malaysia: Islam, society and politics|url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=0W5t5lxigh8C&pg=PA222&dq=Burhanuddin+al-Helmy+matheson+hooker&hl=en&ei=FSohTP3YKMGPcYOe-VQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CC8Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false|year=2003|publisher=Institute of Southeast Asian Studies|isbn=9812301615|page=222}}</ref>

==Asa Usua==
Burhanuddin adalah anak partamo dari pasangan Haji Mohamad Noor jo Sharifah Zaharah bt Habib Osman. Ayahnyo barasa dari [[Batusangka]], [[Sumatera Barat]] nan marantau ka Malaysia pado taun 1908, sadangkan ibunyo barasa dari [[Kota Malaka|Malaka]].

==Kahidupan==
Burhanuddin dilaiaan di Kota Bharu, Perak, Malaysia pado taun 1911, lalu baraja di Universiti Muslim Aligarh di [[India]].<ref name="bio"/><ref name="Leifer">{{cite book|last=Leifer|first=Michael|title=Dictionary of the modern politics of South-East Asia|edition=3rd|year=2001|publisher=Taylor & Francis|isbn=0415238757|page=79}}</ref> Salasai baraja di India jo sapulangnyo dari [[Palestina]] jo [[Turki]], Burhanuddin baliak batugeh sabagai guru [[bahaso Arab]] di Madrasah Aljunied Al-Islamiah, Aljunied, [[Singapura]].

Sasudah [[Parang Dunia II]], Burhanuddin mandirian Parti Kabangsaan Malayu Malaya (PKMM). Partai iko manuntuik kamardekaan panuah untuak [[Samananjuang Malayu]] sarato manantang sagalo bantuak [[Imperium Britania|panjajahan Inggirih]]. Burhanuddin mambao pulo PKMM untuak mawujudan [[Malayu Raya]], yaitu sabuah gagasan kasatuan politik [[Malaysia]]-[[Indonesia]].<ref name="Leifer"/><ref>{{cite book|last=Federspiel|first=Howard M.|title=Sultans, shamans, and saints: Islam and Muslims in Southeast Asia|url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=5Qf39DpguysC&pg=PA177&dq=%22burhanuddin+al-helmy%22&hl=en&ei=YSshTN6CMI2Wca2A2SY&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CE4Q6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=%22burhanuddin%20al-helmy%22&f=false|year=2007|publisher=University of Hawaii Press|isbn=0824830520|page=177}}</ref>

Pado taun 1956 baliau diangkek sabagai pamimpin [[Parti Islam Se-Malaysia]] (PAS),<ref name="Leifer"/> sampai kamatiannyo pado taun 1969.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aliran.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1072:that-complex-entity-called-pas&catid=89:2009-7&Itemid=45|title=That complex entity called Pas|date=14 November 2009|work=Aliran Monthly|accessdate=22 June 2010}}</ref> Di bawah kapimpinannyo, PAS mampunyai orientasi manyokong pagarakan anti-kolonialisme.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/default.asp?page=2008\04\11\story_11-4-2008_pg3_3|title=On the road to change?|last=Farish Noor|date=11 April 2008|work=Daily Times|accessdate=22 June 2010}}</ref> Kapamimpinannyo tapotong dek panangkok-an "Akta Kasalamatan Dalam Nagari" pado taun 1965, lalu salanjuiknyo dipanjaro salamo sataun ateh tuduahan bakomplot untuak mangguliangan pamarentah Malaysia, sarato mambangun sabuah pamarentah pangganti nan labiah ramah kapado Indonesia.<ref name="Leifer"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.google.com.au/newspapers?id=hVMRAAAAIBAJ&sjid=ZpUDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6858,29259&dq=burhanuddin+al-helmy&hl=en|title="Opposition Plan for Rebellion"|date=1 March 1965|work=[[The Age]]|publisher=[[Fairfax Media]]|accessdate=22 June 2010}}</ref>

Burhanuddin maningga dunia pado tanggal 10 Oktober 1969 akibaik panyakik sarato siksaan samaso dalam tahanan ISA.

